title: Why Russell Wilson struggled in return, how the 49ers can make the playoffs + NFC Playoff Picture breakdown (Football 11/17)
description:
Brady Quinn joins Will Brinson as he does every Wednesday to discuss what's happening around the NFL. First, the guys chat about OBJ's debut with the Rams and expectations for LA. Then, BQ breaks down why Russell Wilson looked rough coming back from injury. Next, they take a look at the NFC playoff picture and select who will reach the postseason.

'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
